<plot>'If You Dare' follows a group of children and the adult artists who mentor them in a theater program for at-risk kids. The stories of the children of the Chicago Avenue Project offer a view from inside of the highs and lows, struggles and triumphs involved in a small theater company's efforts to make a difference in the lives of children facing challenges of inner city life.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?256697</url></doc>
